item.title: Greetings!
item.description: Greetings Visitor! So, you have stumbled upon the starting steps of my personal log-book/mind-dump/brain-fart..whatever you might call. Very brave indeed! To get you upto speed, here I will try to respectfully (sometimes hastily) dump the contents of my mind. What content…? Well, to start with, random engineering stories from my daily work. Maybe an icky production bug, or a deep debugging session, or maybe just something new I explored and figured out while on work.
